{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The horde is here. Pick a hunter and defeat the demon invasion! Horde Hunters takes the popular horde survival genre (aka bullet heaven) that Vampire Survivors started to new directions.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>9 characters each with a unique weapon and ability<br></li><li>75+ weapons and items to create your character build and synergies with. Weapons automatically aim and fire however you can manually aim your primary weapon if you want<br></li><li>20+ consumables (instant single-use items) can be picked up and used when needed<br></li><li>13 maps with typically short runs (~15-20min)<br></li><li>5 endless maps with global leaderboards and a custom weekly map to compete in<br></li><li>Maps are procedurally generated to make every run unique. There are unique buildings for you can interact with and various missions and events that keep you busy<br></li><li>During the run you use gold to buy, sell and upgrade your gear. You can also hire party members to your aid<br></li><li>Level up your character and choose from 40+ power-ups to boost your run (meta progression)<br></li><li>20+ hours of content</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Accessible</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Custom difficulty options are available if you find the game too easy or hard<br></li><li>Game speed can be increased if you want more fast-paced runs</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Village win with Nicolaus","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2178560/072c72d30b5de112d87e83bfe8fc3b484037471f.jpg"},{"name":"Village win with Titus","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2178560/d112bab951f3d6c3f72bba3085af85c596e22374.jpg"},{"name":"Village win with Merle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2178560/aec2ce7d2e270bea7d1d17bf84f6df085b463eba.jpg"},{"name":"Village win with Jarvis","path":"ht